Webex App | Turn on hardware acceleration
If your CPU usage is high when you're on a call or in a meeting, turn on hardware acceleration to encode your self-view video more efficiently.
1
Click your profile picture, and then select Settings > Video.
2
Check the Enable hardware acceleration check box.
If your system doesn't support this feature, you won't see this check box.